JOHANNESBURG - Author and journalist Thandeka Gqubule has written a book about former Public Protector Thuli Madonsela.Titled 'No Longer Whispering to Power', the book looks at Madonsela's life, her childhood and her tenure as Public Protector.WATCH: Madonsela looks backThandeka Gqubule and Thuli Madonsela spoke to ENCA's Cathy Mohlalana.*View the attached videoeNCA